As long as a stock is trading on the open market it’s all affected by just psychology thus under- or overvalued hence the forces of Demand VS Supply. Whatever any news they come up with to affect sentiment: I’m not affected by it. Just cut all the noise and just stick tot the chart or spend time understanding advanced TA.
I don’t mind taking a loss if my forecast has any invalidation. All what matters is that I make more money than I lose: which I obviously do if you read many screenshots of locked in gains on my timeline. Never marry an asset: you are trading/investing to make money…
